* Validation\nApproaches
** Pipeline Expectations
***_ During data transformations
***_ Lakeflow Spark Declarative Pipelines
***_ Actions: warn, drop, fail
***_ Real-time quality control
***_ Streaming & materialized views
** Table Constraints
***_ Enforced at write time
***_ Delta Lake tables
***_ Reject invalid data
***_ Batch processing
***_ Strict integrity guarantees
** Quality Dimensions
*** Nullability
****_ Required values must exist
*** Cardinality
****_ Uniqueness where expected
*** Range Checking
****_ Values within bounds
@endmindmap
